name: SUNSET SARSAPARILLA STAR
description:
"Sunset Sarsaparilla star bottle caps are a rare variant of the Sunset Sarsaparilla bottle cap, featuring a blue star on the underside of the cap. The Sunset Sarsaparilla star bottle cap, though dim, glows blue."

Sought out by bottlecap collectors across the Mojave Wasteland making this cap very rare.
